Class EcogridCompressedDataCacheItem

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Runnable, CacheObjectInterface
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EcogridGZippedDataCacheItem, EcogridTarArchivedDataCacheItem, EcogridZippedDataCacheItem

    public abstract class EcogridCompressedDataCacheItem
extends EcogridDataCacheItem
    This class will handle compressed data object(for example a zip file) download from server in Chache system. This class will encapsulate unzip the zip file into a directory and give a api to user to get a local file path by given a file entension. For example: a zip file will be download as 1209.dat(it has xyz.bil, xyz.blw, xyz.hdr, xyz.stx)then the zip file will be unzziped to /cachedir/uncompress/1029.dat. If you give a file extension - bil, it will return /cachedir/uncompress/l029.dat/xyz.bil
    Author:
    Jing Tao
